org.mini2Dx.core.graphics.pipeline

Class RenderFrameBufferOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.core.graphics.pipeline.RenderFrameBufferOperation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RenderOperation

    public class RenderFrameBufferOperation
extends java.lang.Object
implements RenderOperation
    Renders a FrameBuffer at 0,0 during the apply(org.mini2Dx.core.game.GameContainer, org.mini2Dx.core.graphics.Graphics) phase. If you want to change the rendering coordinate, extend this class and override the updateRenderPosition(Vector2, GameContainer, float) method
